title: 1 BR w/ Private Terrace!! ** 2/5 TRAINS, Amenities!
posting_body: ['Half months broker fee', 'September 1st move in date', 'Text Lihi @ 3477484234 w/ address 937 Rogers', 'Large and super sunny penthouse apartment with private outdoor deck!', 'Prime location near Prospect Park, Brand New Luxury Elevator Building with Recreational Room, GYM, Laundry Room, bike storage, Car Garage Parking, Elevator, Extra Storage Units and Awesome Rooftop Access!', 'Located on Rogers Ave and Tilden St, right off the Church Ave 2 & 5 trains, short walk to the B & Q lines and Prospect Park!', 'The Parade Grounds and So much more.', 'Incredible neighborhood on the border Of Prospect Lefferts Gardens!', 'Private large outdoor deck Modern kitchen complete with Dishwasher / Microwave / Gas Stoves and all Stainless steel appliances Spacious bedroom with windows and closets Large modern tiled bathroom with glass wall and deep tub / shower A true delight this apartment is with high ceilings, hardwood floors, and so much light and open space!', 'All brand new!', 'Great closets too!', 'Guarantors Accepted Laundry Room in the building Pets allowed *upon approval Dishwasher Gym Balcony Roof Deck Central air and heat Parking Elevator Bike Room Package Room Showing by appointment - Half months broker fee due at signing']
